'''約瑟夫·麥可·梅爾科拉'''（{{lang-en|Joseph Michael Mercola}}，{{bd|1954年|7月8日|||}}）是美国[[替代医学|另類醫學]]的倡导者以及骨科醫生，同時他亦销售醫療補給品和[[医疗器械|醫療器械]]， <ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Dr. Mercola: Visionary or Quack?|url=http://www.chicagomag.com/Chicago-Magazine/February-2012/Dr-Joseph-Mercola-Visionary-or-Quack/|accessdate=2020-03-08|author=Smith|date=January 31, 2012|first=Bryan|work=Chicago magazine|language=en|archive-date=2020-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200307060324/https://www.chicagomag.com/Chicago-Magazine/February-2012/Dr-Joseph-Mercola-Visionary-or-Quack/|dead-url=no}}</ref>其產品存在不少争议。2013年為止， <ref>{{Cite web|title=Dr. Mercola's Natural Health Center|url=http://www.natural-health-center.com/|accessdate=March 19, 2014|publisher=www.natural-health-center.com|archive-date=2014-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316084201/http://www.natural-health-center.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 梅爾科拉在[[绍姆堡_(伊利诺伊州)|伊利诺伊州]]经营着“ Dr. Mercola Natural Health Center”。 <ref name="Gumpert">{{Cite web|title=Old-Time Sales Tricks on the Net|url=http://www.businessweek.com/smallbiz/content/may2006/sb20060523_063274.htm|accessdate=September 1, 2009|author=Gumpert|date=May 23, 2006|first=David|work=[[BusinessWeek|BusinessWeek]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090706135749/http://www.businessweek.com/smallbiz/content/may2006/sb20060523_063274.htm|archivedate=2009-07-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>他編寫了了''《無穀物飲食》（暫譯）'' <ref>{{Cite news|title=Doc's got odd appetite|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2003-05-25/news/0305250393_1_food-pyramid-diet-guru-osteopathic|accessdate=August 22, 2011|work=Chicago Tribune|date=May 25, 2003|archive-date=2012-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206180716/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2003-05-25/news/0305250393_1_food-pyramid-diet-guru-osteopathic|dead-url=no}}</ref> （與 Alison Rose Levy共同編寫）以及《大鳥流感骗局》（暫譯）等書籍。

梅爾科拉及其同事經常在網際網路上倡导了许多未经廣泛證實效果的替代健康概念，包括[[顺势疗法|顺势疗法]]和[[接種疫苗爭議|反对]][[疫苗接種|接种疫苗]]。此類想法經常受到諸多攻擊。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=A major funder of the anti-vaccine movement has made millions selling natural health products|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/investigations/2019/10/15/fdc01078-c29c-11e9-b5e4-54aa56d5b7ce_story.html|accessdate=2020-03-08|author=Satija|date=December 20, 2019|first=Neena|work=Washington Post|language=en|archive-date=2019-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191221004449/https://www.washingtonpost.com/investigations/2019/10/15/fdc01078-c29c-11e9-b5e4-54aa56d5b7ce_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>梅爾科拉是美国医师與外科医生协会（Association of American Physician and Surgeons ）的成员之一，该組織致力於為另類治療方式提供更多科學證據。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Who Sits at the Clintons' Table, and Who Picks Up the Tab?|url=http://www.aapsonline.org/newsletters/apr94.htm|accessdate=2011-08-19|date=1994-04-01|publisher=[[Association_of_American_Physicians_and_Surgeons|Association of American Physicians and Surgeons]]|archive-date=2011-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927001608/http://www.aapsonline.org/newsletters/apr94.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

